+/// Network guard: Plaid manifest restricts all operations to three exact hosts:
+/// `production.plaid.com`, `sandbox.plaid.com`, `development.plaid.com`.
+/// Verify that allowed hosts pass and non-matching hosts are denied.
+#[test]
